lculations for the\nfour-parameter law for the passbands listed above, and compared them with those\nfrom the power-2 law. Comparisons between the quality of the fits provided by\nthe power-2 and four-parameter laws show that the latter presents a lower merit\nfunction, $\\chi^2$, than the former for both cases (M1 and M2). This is\nimportant when choosing the best approach for a particular science goal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 18:15:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-04"}
