ong the superconducting interface. Our findings mark a critical milestone\nalong the path to explore correlated and fractional QH-based superconducting\ndevices that should host non-Abelian Majorana and parafermion zero modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 20:13:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-04"}
