lyzed. This work lays the foundation for future developments\nin the field of ambipolar dual-gate TMD transistors, showing their potential\nfor low-power, high-speed and more flexible logic circuits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 21:38:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
